{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Do you want to play an RPG with your friends but don\u2019t have 1000 hours to grind? You like complex card games, but don\u2019t want to read a novel every time you see a new card? Wanna combo off so hard you might blow up yourself? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Well, <strong>Shuffle Quest</strong>\u2019s got you covered! Shuffling up the complex strategy of <strong>card battlers</strong>, the endless replayability of <strong>roguelites</strong> and the untamed chaos of a <strong>co-op RPG</strong> is a sure-fire way to slay the princess, save the dragon and be back at the tavern before happy hour!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192980/extras/Lucy_Stab.gif?t=1733925843\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192980/extras/Co_op.png?t=1733925843\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0Take the role of a party of roguish adventurers in a quest to loot every corner of Boardia\u2019s frontier!<strong> Play with your friends</strong> or <strong>manage the party</strong> all on your own.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192980/extras/Team_Attack.gif?t=1733925843\" /></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192980/extras/Deckbuilding.png?t=1733925843\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0Each character in the game has strengths and weaknesses, but none can triumph on their own. <strong>Joining the power of four decks</strong> the combo potential is unlimited.</p><p class=\